u</h2>\n      <h1 class=\"about-hero__title\">Mánu Fosela</h1>\n      <p class=\"about-hero__subtitle\">Desarrollador, formador y apasionado de la tecnología desde hace más de 25 años.</p>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- Bio -->\n  <section class=\"about-bio\">\n    <div class=\"about-bio__grid\">\n      <div class=\"about-bio__text\">\n        <h3 class=\"about-bio__heading\">¿Quién soy?</h3>\n        <p>\n          Soy Mánu Fosela, ingeniero de software con más de 25 años de experiencia profesional desarrollando aplicaciones web, liderando equipos técnicos y mentorizando a personas que están empezando en el mundo del desarrollo.\n        </p>\n        <p>\n          He trabajado en proyectos de todo tipo: desde startups hasta grandes empresas, pasando por consultoras y producto propio. He visto nacer la web, crecer JavaScript y evolucionar las herramientas que usamos hoy.\n        </p>\n        <p>\n          Esta plataforma nace de una necesidad real: compartir lo que sé de forma directa, práctica y sin rodeos, con personas cercanas que quieren aprender de verdad.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"about-bio__highlights\">\n        <div class=\"highlight-card\">\n          <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">code</span>\n          <div>\n            <strong>+25 años</strong>\n            <span>desarrollando software</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"highlight-card\">\n          <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">group</span>\n          <div>\n            <strong>+15 años</strong>\n            <span>mentorizando juniors</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"highlight-card\">\n          <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">manage_accounts</span>\n          <div>\n            <strong>+10 años</strong>\n            <span>liderando equipos</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"highlight-card\">\n          <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">school</span>\n          <div>\n            <strong>Formador</strong>\n            <span>en tecnologías web</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- Philosophy -->\n  <section class=\"about-philosophy\">\n    <div class=\"about-philosophy__content\">\n      <h3 class=\"about-philosophy__heading\">Mi filosofía</h3>\n      <div class=\"about-philosophy__grid\">\n        <div class=\"philosophy-card\">\n          <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">construction</span>\n          <h4>Aprender haciendo</h4>\n          <p>Los cursos están basados en proyectos reales. Nada de ejemplos de juguete: construyes cosas que funcionan.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"philosophy-card\">\n          <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">handshake</span>\n          <h4>Cercanía</h4>\n          <p>No soy un avatar detrás de una pantalla. Puedes preguntarme directamente y te respondo yo.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"philosophy-card\">\n          <span class=\"material-symbols-outlined\">visibility</span>\n          <h4>Sin filtros</h4>\n          <p>Te cuento lo que funciona y lo que no, basándome en experiencia real, no en teoría de manual.</p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n  <!-- CTA -->\n  <section class=\"about-cta\">\n    <div class=\"about-cta__content\">\n      <h3 class=\"about-cta__title\">¿Quieres aprender conmigo?</h3>\n      <p class=\"about-cta__text\">Echa un vistazo a los cursos disponibles o solicita acceso si aún no tienes cuenta.</p>\n      <div class=\"about-cta__actions\">\n        <a href=\"/cursos\" class=\"btn btn--primary btn--lg\">Ver cursos</a>\n        <a href=\"/solicitar-acceso\" class=\"btn btn--outline btn--lg\">Solicitar acceso</a>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n\n</MainLayout>\n\n<style>\n  /* --- Hero --- */\n  .about-hero {\n    padding: 4rem var(--section-px) 3rem;\n    background: linear-gradient(to right, #0f172a 0%, #1a2e05 100%);\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n\n  .about-hero__content {\n    max-width: var(--container-max);\n    margin-inline: auto;\n  }\n\n  .about-hero__title {\n    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);\n    font-weight: 900;\n    line-height: 1.1;\n    background: var(--gradient-primary);\n    -webkit-background-clip: text;\n    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;\n    background-clip: text;\n    margin-bottom: 1rem;\n  }\n\n  .about-hero__subtitle {\n    color: #f1f5f9;\n    font-size: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.25rem);\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    opacity: 0.9;\n    max-width: 600px;\n    margin-inline: auto;\n  }\n\n  /* --- Bio --- */\n  .about-bio {\n    padding: var(--section-py) var(--section-px);\n    background-color: var(--color-bg-white);\n  }\n\n  .about-bio__grid {\n    max-width: var(--container-max);\n    margin-inline: auto;\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    gap: 3rem;\n    align-items: start;\n  }\n\n  @media (min-width: 1024px) {\n    .about-bio__grid {\n      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n    }\n  }\n\n  .about-bio__heading {\n    font-size: 2rem;\n    font-weight: 900;\n    color: var(--color-text-primary);\n    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n  }\n\n  .about-bio__text {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 1.25rem;\n  }\n\n  .about-bio__text p {\n    color: var(--color-text-secondary);\n    font-size: 1.125rem;\n    line-height: 1.7;\n  }\n\n  .about-bio__highlights {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 1rem;\n  }\n\n  .highlight-card {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 1rem;\n    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;\n    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);\n    border: 2px solid var(--color-border);\n    background-color: var(--color-bg-white);\n    transition: all var(--transition-base);\n  }\n\n  .highlight-card:hover {\n    border-color: var(--color-primary);\n    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);\n  }\n\n  .highlight-card > .material-symbols-outlined {\n    font-size: 2rem;\n    color: var(--color-primary);\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n  }\n\n  .highlight-card div {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n  }\n\n  .highlight-card strong {\n    font-size: 1.125rem;\n    font-weight: 800;\n    color: var(--color-text-primary);\n  }\n\n  .highlight-card span:not(.material-symbols-outlined) {\n    font-size: 0.875rem;\n    color: var(--color-text-secondary);\n  }\n\n  /* --- Philosophy --- */\n  .about-philosophy {\n    padding: var(--section-py) var(--section-px);\n    background-color: var(--color-bg-slate-50);\n  }\n\n  .about-philosophy__content {\n    max-width: var(--container-max);\n    margin-inline: auto;\n  }\n\n  .about-philosophy__heading {\n    font-size: 2rem;\n    font-weight: 900;\n    color: var(--color-text-primary);\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-bottom: 3rem;\n  }\n\n  .about-philosophy__grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    gap: 2rem;\n  }\n\n  @media (min-width: 768px) {\n    .about-philosophy__grid {\n      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n    }\n  }\n\n  .philosophy-card {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 1rem;\n    padding: 2rem;\n    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);\n    border: 2px solid var(--color-border);\n    background-color: var(--color-bg-white);\n    transition: all var(--transition-base);\n  }\n\n  .philosophy-card:hover {\n    box-shadow: var(--shadow-2xl);\n    border-color: var(--color-primary);\n  }\n\n  .philosophy-card > .material-symbols-outlined {\n    font-size: 2rem;\n    color: var(--color-secondary);\n  }\n\n  .philosophy-card h4 {\n    font-size: 1.25rem;\n    font-weight: 700;\n    color: var(--color-text-primary);\n  }\n\n  .philosophy-card p {\n    color: var(--color-text-secondary);\n    line-height: 1.7;\n  }\n\n  /* --- CTA --- */\n  .about-cta {\n    padding: var(--section-py) var(--section-px);\n    background: linear-gradient(to right, #0f172a 0%, #1a2e05 100%);\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n\n  .about-cta__content {\n    max-width: 600px;\n    margin-inline: auto;\n  }\n\n  .about-cta__title {\n    font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);\n    font-weight: 900;\n    background: var(--gradient-primary);\n    -webkit-background-clip: text;\n    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;\n    background-clip: text;\n    margin-bottom: 1rem;\n  }\n\n  .about-cta__text {\n    color: #f1f5f9;\n    font-size: 1.125rem;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    opacity: 0.9;\n    margin-bottom: 2rem;\n  }\n\n  .about-cta__actions {\n    display: flex;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n    gap: 1rem;\n    justify-content: center;\n  }\n</style>\n","numLines":319,"startLine":1,"totalLines":319}}} (stream=stdout)
